snippet.title: 13 of 100 3 laws perfect Police wrongful death
snippet.description:
This is a great video for today since we get to see part of it play out in the Amber Guyger case.  However, the basis for this video is to illustrate how the laws of robotics actually shows the actual responsibility of police officers to the public they swore to protect
